  <div class='container'>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <h1>Made-To-Measure Blinds</h1>
        <h2></h2>
        <p class='big'>
          Choosing blinds gives you a stylish way to control light, temperature and privacy. And that’s exactly what you need to create a relaxing retreat for spring, summer, autumn and winter.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <img src="/images/photos/conservatory_blinds.jpg" alt="" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <p>
          Whether you are looking to completely refurbish the office or just add a stylish touch to your home, a blind can go a very long way towards making your interior appear stylish and modern. Our blinds are perfect for providing privacy while still keeping a room bright and breezy. Here at Easy-Fit, we make each of our blinds to your exact specification.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>





<section class='page-section left '>
  <div class='container'>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-6 ">
        
  <img src="/images/Vertical-Conservatory-Blinds.jpg" alt="" />
  <img src="/images/brown-vertical-blind-office-kelis-copper_980_x_336.jpg" alt="" />

      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 ">
        
  <h2>Vertical Blinds</h2>
  <h3>Providing the perfect balance of light and privacy.</h3>
  <p>
    Our made-to-measure Vertical blinds offer style and practicality, providing the perfect balance of light and privacy. Fingertip control over shading levels allows sunlight to gently filter into your room, while keeping prying eyes out.
  </p>

  <div class="benefits">
    <p>
      <h3><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Sheer, PVC and flame retardant fabrics</h3>
    </p>
    <p>
      <h3><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Curved headrails available for bay or bow windows</h3>
    </p>
    <p>
      <h3><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Can be made to fit sloping windows</h3>
    </p>
    <p>
      <h3><i class="fa fa-check"></i> A simple wand operates the blind</h3>
    </p>
  </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>





<section class='page-section right '>
  <div class='container'>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-6  col-md-push-6 ">
        
  <img src="/images/hillarysblinds_8038679v1_980_x_336.jpg" alt="" />
  <img src="/images/hillarysblinds_8039130v1_980_x_336.jpg" alt="" />

      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6  col-md-pull-6 ">
        
  <h2>Conservatory Roof Blinds</h2>
  <h3>Keep the heat in, or out.</h3>
  <p>
    In summer, sunshine will blaze through a conservatory roof; while in winter, heat rises and escapes through the same ceiling. Our specialist fabrics can help moderate these extremes, so you can enjoy your conservatory in all conditions.
  </p>

  <div class="benefits">
    <p>
      <h3><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Gorgeous range, with styles to match your interior</h3>
    </p>
    <p>
      <h3><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Specialist finishes help reflect the sun’s heat</h3>
    </p>
    <p>
      <h3><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Creates an effective insulating layer in winter</h3>
    </p>
    <p>
      <h3><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Snug feel for getting cosy on cold days</h3>
    </p>
  </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>








<section class='page-section left texture'>
