  <h2>Roman Blinds</h2>
  <h3>Classic and luxurious.</h3>
  <p>
    Romans are perfectly practical as well as supremely stylish. A choice of lining including our standard option, blackout and thermal is available as well as control chains in a variety of colours to suit the rest of your décor.
  </p>

  <div class="benefits">
    <p>
      <h3><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Sophisticated styles with a luxurious feel</h3>
    </p>
    <p>
      <h3><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Fully-lined as standard, with a choice of lining</h3>
    </p>
    <p>
      <h3><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Customise with metal control chains</h3>
    </p>
  </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>






